{"tid":2287150,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港]拜登派 陣營指引！","createTime":"2020-11-15T14:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T06:24:52.000Z","uid":241151,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"df8c327c6dc9103a6fbe5229d7dcff61913ba73e","tid":2287150,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T14:02:48.000Z","msg":"拜登派：<br />\n<br />\n所有藍絲及建制傳媒，蘋果日報，立場新聞，泛民(民主黨，公民黨，工黨，街工，新民主同盟，人民力量，社民連)<br />\n<br />\n另外同泛民及蘋果有關係既團體及人物：<br />\n<br />\n泛民初選時歸邊：青年新政，本土民主前線(包括梁天琦)，所有港獨派<br />\n<br />\n與政府站在同一立場，在網絡鼓吹防疫周圍散播恐懼的媒體(拜登是推崇以防疫之名操控及壓迫市民)：<br />\n<br />\n啤梨晚報(林匡正最為主動)，myradio，JFFT，Japhk，丘品，花生台，D100<br />\n<br />\n最近忽然轉軚支持拜登的網絡媒體： 連登，高登<br />\n<br />\n以上全屬於支持拜登與及通共匪的陣營，實際上不會支持特朗普"},{"pid":"a6f9c2d429b89a0fdebaaf8582ff8777cc977f3a","tid":2287150,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T01:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff67a33153004d05096fe1b3a417f39a4a99d49","tid":2287150,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T02:01:38.000Z","msg":"沒有民主黨營 沒有共和黨營 只有拜登營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157a13db57f1d99f993102dada30ef5f80efc9aa","tid":2287150,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T02:18:02.000Z","msg":"樓主既STU = Support TrUmp <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5afa37b8e9ba17321917806c4ccb03103201a302","tid":2287150,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T06:24:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c239f4d7a764a18b0e5779312b307a6ee47ed5","tid":2287150,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"157a13db57f1d99f993102dada30ef5f80efc9aa","tid":2287150,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T02:18:02.000Z","msg":"樓主既STU = Support TrU